{
  "texts": [
    "Such endeavors are made to provide established resources of GAN's effectiveness to the growing application areas where GANs are being accepted and tried currently.",
    "This review too, has been worked to serve the same purpose and accordingly provides scrutiny of articles that talk about new and traditional GAN variants.",
    "Several GAN variants are developed as enhancements of the base GAN model to eliminate its limitations of instability and complexities at the time of model training.",
    "The variants developed and are evaluated many times to identify the prime potentialities and scope of further improvements.The state-of-the-art GANs, which included base GAN, WGAN, Semi-GAN, C-GAN, LS-GAN, BiGAN, AC-GAN, InfoGAN, SeqGAN, and BEGAN, were reviewed and summarized by Gou et al. [15] concluding that GANs have a lot of potential for virtual-real interaction and integration in parallel systems research.",
    "Their experiment demonstrated that GANs provide significant algorithmic assistance for parallel intelligence.This section presents the works that are most related to different architectures listed as Pix-2pix, Cycle-GAN, DC-GAN, BIGGAN, PGGAN etc."
  ]
}